comp/nonebot.enter: Send {cmd} to confirm the prompt as the input
comp/nonebot.exit: Send {cmd} to exit the completion session
comp/nonebot.other: Input which not in above will be confirmed as the input
comp/nonebot.timeout: Completion session timed out. Exited automatically

nbp-alc.log.discord_ambiguous_subcommand: Subcommand {name} which have both Args and sub Option/Subcommand can make unintended consequences when you translate Alconna to Discord slash-command
nbp-alc.error.discord_prefix: The Alconna obj must have '/' prefix when use to translate to Discord slash-command
nbp-alc.error.extension_forbid_exclude: Extension which id starts with '!' cannot be excluded
nbp-alc.error.extension_path_load: Value of {path} is not a subclass of Extension
nbp-alc.error.extension_path_invalid: {path} is not a valid extension path
